OL,5, The theatre company behind a new West  
OL,6, End production of Romeo and Juliet has 
OL,7, condemned the "deplorable racial abuse"
OL,8, directed towards one of its stars.     
OL,10,FThe show, which features Spider-Man    
OL,11,Factor Tom Holland as Romeo, unveiled   
OL,12,Fits full cast last week, including     
OL,13,FFrancesca Amewudah-Rivers as Juliet.   
OL,15,FOn Friday, the Jamie Lloyd Company said
OL,16,Fthere had been "a barrage of deplorable
OL,17,Fracial abuse online directed towards a 
OL,18,Fmember of our company".                
OL,20,F"This must stop," a statement said.    
